{"tid":2408712,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳市政府為樓市定價，全市業主身家縮水三成！","createTime":"2021-02-15T08:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T11:46:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce8dabacb8851ddf0d5d64f8e334849e2b854de","tid":2408712,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0DM2GLnsKY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0DM2GLnsKY0&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=cdc5f65a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0DM2GLnsKY0</a>"},{"pid":"17859009cb1545682ea071a2a69435d5d60a1714","tid":2408712,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:03:48.000Z","msg":"中國樓市】深圳二手房參考價普遍打7折 其他城市會跟嗎？<br />\n<br />\n深圳市8日宣布建立「二手住房成交參考價格發布機制」，3,595個小區標價普遍打7折。業內人士分析，此措施重在引導商業銀行合理發放二手住房貸款。易居研究院智庫中心研究總監嚴躍進認為，預計隨著深圳此次二手房價格數據披露後，全國其他城市也會積極跟進，值得期待。<br />\n<br />\n今日早間，內媒發現，多間房產中介已針對新政作出緊急調整。截至發稿，鏈家已下線所有深圳在售二手房源的掛牌價，數量多達近32,000套，此外，各個小區掛牌均價也無法查詢。Q房網同樣下線超28,000套在售二手房源的掛牌價，但依然可以查詢到小區2月參考均價和掛牌均價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2874857/【中國樓市】深圳二手房參考價普遍打7折%20其他城市會跟嗎？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2874857%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E3%80%91%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%88%BF%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83%E5%83%B9%E6%99%AE%E9%81%8D%E6%89%937%E6%8A%98%2520%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%83%E8%B7%9F%E5%97%8E%EF%BC%9F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=bd69699c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2874857/【中國樓市】深圳二手房參考價普遍打7折%20其他城市會跟嗎？</a>"},{"pid":"e4a8dd6418d96b142bb5b07b3d5838f684e4a944","tid":2408712,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g2rjOcR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg2rjOcR.png&